			<h2 class="cs-archive-title">doing the dmca shuffle</h2>
					</div>
	<div class="post-10217703 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-uncategorized tag-doing-the-dmca-shuffle tag-dmca tag-copyright tag-lawsuits tag-universal-music tag-universal-music-group tag-youtube tag-eff entry longform-archive-entry">	<header class="entry-header">
